msgid "Answers tab"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys/time_random.rst:133
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Answers` tab **only** appears if the selected "
":guilabel:`Question Type` provides answer options to the participant."
